The <code>setTargetAtTime()</code> method of the <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/API/AudioParam" title="The Web Audio API's AudioParam interface represents an audio-related parameter, usually a parameter of an AudioNode (such as GainNode.gain)."><code>AudioParam</code></a> interface schedules the start of a gradual change to the <code>AudioParam</code> value. This is useful for decay or release portions of ADSR envelopes.